Rating: 3
I made this for my husband and I and it is really good. Pretty simple to make too. I beat the egg a little before putting in with the greens. I used 1/4 teaspoon of anchovy paste and could have used more. For the blue cheese I used crumbled gorgonzola. I didn't make the croutons.

