I'm all for adapting classics and I love blue cheese, but I thought this was a bit heavy handed for a salad (egg, anchovy, parmesan, blue cheese...???) I may try omitting the egg next time and just lightly sprinkle a bit of blue cheese on top instead of adding to the dressing. We'll see! That said, my spouse really enjoyed it.

