Rating: 4
One of my favorite restaurants makes a salad called "Black and Blue Caesar" which is this salad topped with strips of grilled rare sirloin. The combination of flavors is amazing. The salad is wonderful on its own, but try it with steak - a carnivore's delight. (PS - I'm not the same reviewer as below from East Lansing, but we apparently like blue cheese and Caesars around here!)

